00:23:31,760 --> 00:23:32,320
predatory.

565
00:23:32,580 --> 00:23:33,700
Alex knows immediately.

566
00:23:33,700 --> 00:23:35,220
These aren't friendlies

567
00:23:35,220 --> 00:23:36,000
coming to help.

568
00:23:38,900 --> 00:23:40,460
Their gear is a Frankenstein

569
00:23:40,460 --> 00:23:42,120
mashup of high-end helmets,

570
00:23:42,420 --> 00:23:42,860
comms,

571
00:23:42,940 --> 00:23:43,800
and lightweight armor.

572
00:23:44,080 --> 00:23:44,920
One guy's pants

573
00:23:44,920 --> 00:23:45,600
are tucked into

574
00:23:45,600 --> 00:23:46,940
his Converse All-Stars.

575
00:23:47,940 --> 00:23:48,980
Does this sound at all

576
00:23:48,980 --> 00:23:50,180
like military to you?

577
00:23:52,180 --> 00:23:54,060
Two men beeline for him

578
00:23:54,060 --> 00:23:55,780
as the third heads up a hill

579
00:23:55,780 --> 00:23:57,120
and shoulders a rifle

580
00:23:57,120 --> 00:23:58,760
aimed at Alex's skull.

581
00:23:58,940 --> 00:24:00,200
And then something happens

582
00:24:00,200 --> 00:24:01,940
that chills Alex's blood.

583
00:24:01,940 --> 00:24:03,480
They call him by name.

584
00:24:04,040 --> 00:24:04,640
Alex!

585
00:24:06,480 --> 00:24:07,980
His stomach drops.

586
00:24:08,720 --> 00:24:10,380
That's when things go sideways.

587
00:24:12,100 --> 00:24:13,780
They rip the rifle from him

588
00:24:13,780 --> 00:24:14,600
and break it down

589
00:24:14,600 --> 00:24:15,400
like a pit crew

590
00:24:15,400 --> 00:24:16,460
