591
00:24:23,080 --> 00:24:24,700
Don't even fucking blink, bro.

592
00:24:26,360 --> 00:24:28,140
He's outgunned three to one

593
00:24:28,140 --> 00:24:29,300
with a rifle pointed

594
00:24:29,300 --> 00:24:30,440
directly at his head

595
00:24:30,440 --> 00:24:31,200
from elevation.

596
00:24:31,200 --> 00:24:36,800
They blindfold Alex

597
00:24:36,800 --> 00:24:38,320
and zip-tie his wrists.

598
00:24:39,060 --> 00:24:40,080
One of them pulls out

599
00:24:40,080 --> 00:24:41,780
a strange handheld device,

600
00:24:42,360 --> 00:24:44,360
something like a bioscanner.

601
00:24:44,700 --> 00:24:46,060
He sweeps Alex with it

602
00:24:46,060 --> 00:24:46,980
from head to toe.

603
00:24:50,520 --> 00:24:52,820
A wand hunting for trackers

604
00:24:52,820 --> 00:24:54,120
and biometric chips?

605
00:24:54,360 --> 00:24:56,460
These guys are professionally trained,

606
00:24:56,640 --> 00:24:58,360
not random desert smugglers.

607
00:24:58,360 --> 00:24:59,960
He doesn't have it.

608
00:24:59,960 --> 00:25:00,900
He doesn't have it.

609
00:25:03,900 --> 00:25:05,300
Man one steps close.

610
00:25:05,800 --> 00:25:07,400
Man three holds the high ground,

611
00:25:07,740 --> 00:25:08,400
rifle steady.

612
00:25:08,980 --> 00:25:10,520
Man one raises his hand,

613
00:25:10,940 --> 00:25:12,040
gives a silent signal,

614
00:25:12,480 --> 00:25:13,860
and somewhere above,

615
00:25:14,200 --> 00:25:15,340
