616
00:25:15,340 --> 00:25:21,760
A 7.62 round tears through Alex's right shoulder,

617
00:25:22,020 --> 00:25:23,460
clavicle pulverized,

618
00:25:23,460 --> 00:25:25,120
shattering bone and flesh.

619
00:25:25,120 --> 00:25:27,780
A second signal and a second shot.

620
00:25:27,780 --> 00:25:29,340
His throat explodes,

621
00:25:29,780 --> 00:25:31,600
