622
00:25:31,600 --> 00:25:36,380
A third signal.

623
00:25:36,380 --> 00:25:37,520
Third shot.

624
00:25:37,760 --> 00:25:38,900
His face is obliterated.

625
00:25:39,160 --> 00:25:40,380
His body drops back,

626
00:25:40,620 --> 00:25:41,900
cold, lifeless,

627
00:25:42,320 --> 00:25:43,360
face to the stars.

628
00:25:43,980 --> 00:25:45,340
Or what's left of his face,

629
00:25:45,420 --> 00:25:45,900
