630
00:25:45,900 --> 00:25:50,500
The entire universe of Alex McEwen

631
00:25:50,500 --> 00:25:52,440
blinked out like a dying star,

632
00:25:52,740 --> 00:25:53,760
sudden and violent.

633
00:25:54,160 --> 00:25:55,540
Children bury their faces.

634
00:25:56,040 --> 00:25:57,780
Some of the women don't look away.

635
00:25:58,180 --> 00:26:00,380
It's almost as if they've seen worse.

636
00:26:00,880 --> 00:26:01,740
Alex McEwen,

637
00:26:02,140 --> 00:26:03,100
tier one operator,

638
00:26:03,500 --> 00:26:03,940
patriot,

639
00:26:04,320 --> 00:26:05,440
