641
00:26:06,680 --> 00:26:13,180
He believed he died serving his country.

642
00:26:13,180 --> 00:26:14,640
But the men who killed him

643
00:26:14,640 --> 00:26:16,860
were clearly serving something else.

644
00:26:25,620 --> 00:26:27,680
Cut to Pope Air Force Base,

645
00:26:27,940 --> 00:26:28,660
North Carolina.

646
00:26:28,880 --> 00:26:29,800
We're inside

647
00:26:29,800 --> 00:26:31,780
Joint Special Operations Command,

648
00:26:32,100 --> 00:26:32,880
or JSOC,

649
00:26:33,120 --> 00:26:34,240
their operations center.

650
00:26:34,240 --> 00:26:37,120
Everyone's frozen.

651
00:26:37,660 --> 00:26:39,400
The Secretary of Defense himself

652
00:26:39,400 --> 00:26:41,200
is on the other end of the call.

653
00:26:41,860 --> 00:26:43,620
And he is not happy.

654
00:26:44,540 --> 00:26:46,400
Dale, what in the fuck

655
00:26:46,400 --> 00:26:47,720
just happened out there?

656
00:26:48,560 --> 00:26:50,100
General Dale Steinmaker,

657
00:26:50,400 --> 00:26:52,520
commander of Joint Special Operations Command,

658
00:26:52,740 --> 00:26:54,620
is wondering the exact same thing.

659
00:26:54,840 --> 00:26:56,200
Uh, Mr. Secretary,

660
00:26:56,500 --> 00:26:58,540
do you have agency guys

661
00:26:58,540 --> 00:27:00,420
in Coyame, Mexico?

662
00:27:01,080 --> 00:27:02,960
Why the fuck would I?

663
00:27:03,140 --> 00:27:04,200
Everyone's at war.

664
00:27:04,420 --> 00:27:05,060
Nobody should have been

665
00:27:05,060 --> 00:27:06,540
in goddamn Mexico.

666
00:27:07,540 --> 00:27:08,900
But the drone feed

667
00:27:08,900 --> 00:27:10,200
tells a different story.

668
00:27:10,700 --> 00:27:11,980
Someone just took out

669
00:27:11,980 --> 00:27:13,860
an entire special mission unit

670
00:27:13,860 --> 00:27:15,400
on JSOC's watch.

671
00:27:15,760 --> 00:27:16,820
The Predator drone

672
00:27:16,820 --> 00:27:18,960
had caught the whole ugly scene.

673
00:27:19,620 --> 00:27:20,780
Alex's execution,

674
00:27:21,360 --> 00:27:22,900
the refugees being loaded

675
00:27:22,900 --> 00:27:24,160
into the shipping container,

676
00:27:24,340 --> 00:27:25,640
and now the helicopters

677
00:27:25,640 --> 00:27:27,320
lifting off into the desert,

678
00:27:27,660 --> 00:27:29,240
human cargo in tow.

679
00:27:29,240 --> 00:27:30,500
Are you suggesting

680
00:27:30,500 --> 00:27:31,700
