681
00:27:32,700 --> 00:27:34,380
Black on block, sir.

682
00:27:35,120 --> 00:27:36,300
Excuse me, gentlemen.

683
00:27:39,580 --> 00:27:41,520
The difference here matters.

684
00:27:41,780 --> 00:27:43,520
Blue on blue is friendly fire.

685
00:27:43,860 --> 00:27:45,400
Tragic, but explainable.

686
00:27:45,840 --> 00:27:47,400
Black on black is a nightmare.

687
00:27:47,800 --> 00:27:48,760
Covert operators

688
00:27:48,760 --> 00:27:50,280
killing covert operators.

689
00:27:50,660 --> 00:27:51,900
Shadow versus shadow.

690
00:27:52,360 --> 00:27:53,340
Whoever did this

691
00:27:53,340 --> 00:27:54,780
wasn't supposed to be there.

692
00:27:54,780 --> 00:27:55,960
The thermal signatures

693
00:27:55,960 --> 00:27:57,120
of six bodies

694
00:27:57,120 --> 00:27:58,560
cool in the sand.

695
00:27:59,600 --> 00:28:01,160
The combat controller

696
00:28:01,160 --> 00:28:02,380
called for air support,

697
00:28:02,700 --> 00:28:03,520
but bled out

698
00:28:03,520 --> 00:28:04,640
mid-sentence.

699
00:28:04,640 --> 00:28:12,280
All right, Vector F-18s

700
00:28:12,280 --> 00:28:13,220
out of white sands.

701
00:28:13,380 --> 00:28:14,960
I want every eye in the sky

702
00:28:14,960 --> 00:28:16,060
on those helicopters.

703
00:28:16,700 --> 00:28:17,560
Wherever they're going,

704
00:28:17,800 --> 00:28:18,900
