707
00:28:25,800 --> 00:28:27,700
Half a dozen airborne assets

708
00:28:27,700 --> 00:28:29,600
spin up in Vector South.

709
00:28:29,600 --> 00:28:32,920
Restricted Area 5107,

710
00:28:33,200 --> 00:28:34,880
the largest military installation

711
00:28:34,880 --> 00:28:35,660
in America.

712
00:28:35,920 --> 00:28:37,600
3,200 square miles

713
00:28:37,600 --> 00:28:40,060
of nothing but sand and secrets.

714
00:28:40,640 --> 00:28:42,660
This is where they detonated Trinity,

715
00:28:43,100 --> 00:28:44,520
the first atomic bomb.

716
00:28:45,220 --> 00:28:47,140
July 16th, 1945.

717
00:28:49,140 --> 00:28:50,060
Since then,

718
00:28:50,200 --> 00:28:51,920
it's been a war game's wasteland.

719
00:28:55,920 --> 00:28:57,360
Eagle One and Eagle Two.

720
00:28:57,360 --> 00:28:58,880
Top Gun graduates

721
00:28:58,880 --> 00:29:00,200
