726
00:29:06,060 --> 00:29:06,860
Sorry, gang.

727
00:29:06,920 --> 00:29:07,980
We're fast, but not fatal.

728
00:29:08,480 --> 00:29:09,360
Negative for ordnance.

729
00:29:09,640 --> 00:29:10,800
How about a show of force instead?

730
00:29:11,440 --> 00:29:11,920
Translation?

731
00:29:12,340 --> 00:29:13,440
Scare the hell out of them

732
00:29:13,440 --> 00:29:14,700
and force them to land.

733
00:29:15,480 --> 00:29:16,480
Just don't kill them.

734
00:29:16,720 --> 00:29:17,660
They want answers,

735
00:29:18,040 --> 00:29:18,720
not corpses.

736
00:29:25,380 --> 00:29:26,400
Five miles out,

737
00:29:26,400 --> 00:29:27,620
the helicopters dropped

738
00:29:27,620 --> 00:29:28,400
into a descent.

739
00:29:28,720 --> 00:29:30,340
They sink below the canyon walls

740
00:29:30,340 --> 00:29:31,040
and vanish.

741
00:29:33,760 --> 00:29:35,060
Back in the war room,

742
00:29:35,340 --> 00:29:36,900
