743
00:29:37,200 --> 00:29:38,500
They lost radar contact.

744
00:29:38,960 --> 00:29:41,000
Radar is line-of-sight technology.

745
00:29:41,420 --> 00:29:42,520
Terrain blocks it.

746
00:29:42,900 --> 00:29:43,740
Fly low enough,

747
00:29:44,080 --> 00:29:45,380
hug the Earth tight enough,

748
00:29:45,620 --> 00:29:46,360
