754
00:29:55,960 --> 00:29:58,380
Eagle One drops to 8,000 feet.

755
00:29:59,980 --> 00:30:01,880
Night vision goggles on.

756
00:30:02,360 --> 00:30:02,860
Scanning.

757
00:30:02,860 --> 00:30:09,020
Bingo.

758
00:30:09,020 --> 00:30:11,320
