770
00:30:33,320 --> 00:30:34,680
This is a United's Navy F-18.

771
00:30:34,940 --> 00:30:36,260
You are instructed to land immediately.

772
00:30:37,160 --> 00:30:39,340
But the helicopters hold course,

773
00:30:39,660 --> 00:30:41,100
